1.4
log
@Make ssh-ask-pass Xinerama aware (also works with XRandR thanks to
its pseudo-Xinerama emulation). ok stsp@@
@
text
@/* x11-ssh-askpass.h:  A generic X11-based password dialog for OpenSSH.
